entry.title: I wish I had more posts in here!

link.title: I wish I had more posts in here!

entry.content: I used to have a blog called datavisualised.com. I had many posts in there and had a lot of fun making them. I stopped posting there because.. life.. and eventually deleted the blog. I wish I didn’t now. I wish I had more posts in here.
